Inferno was frustrated at seeing his timed shot miss.  Then 
detecting the transmission he knew that there would be more of these 
guys.
"We must report back to the royalty!"  He set his gun for 
flamethrower and fired up to create a smokescreen.

Quickstrike and grabbed Waspinator's head and they retreated.
